	This charming cushion is made with pink polkadot fabric around the edge and other various colours of fabric on a brown and white polkadot base. The cushion is decorated with a pink polkadot bow and brown letters in the centre reading &lsquo;I love you more than chocolate&rsquo;. This lovely cushion is then stuffed with cotton wool to make it soft and fluffy for the extra loveliness. This cute cushion would make the perfect gift for someone special to show them how much you love them, which must be a lot if it is really more than you love chocolate! This decorative cushion would also make the perfect housewarming present for your loved one and would look good put on a shelf, mantelpiece or windowsill in any room throughout the home including bedrooms, living rooms and hallways. The cushion measures 18cm long and 14cm wide.</p>
